verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
His name is exalted far above the earth
His name is higher than the heavens
His name is exalted far above the earth
In glory and honour and praise unto his name

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
No other name but the name of Jesus
No other name but the name of the Lord
No other name but the name of Jesus
Is worthy of glory
Is worthy of honour
Is worthy of power and of praise
